strings: Plot a Graph of the Settings

Make an image of Coupled-Map Lattice (CML). CML is a kind of Cellula Automata on continuous (value) domain. In GIMP_RUN_NONINTERACTIVE, the name of a prameter file is passed as the 4th arg. You can control CML_explorer via parameter file.
; This is a parameter file for CML_explorer
Error: it's not CML parameter file.
Warning: '%s' is an old format file.
Warning: '%s' is a parameter file for a newer version of CML Explorer.
Seed of Random (only for "From Seed" Modes)
Switch to "From seed" With the Last Seed
"Fix seed" button is an alias of me.
The same seed produces the same image, if (1) the widths of images are same (this is the reason why image on drawable is different from preview), and (2) all mutation rates equal to zero.
Warning: the source and the destination are the same channel.
The name of parameter file. CML_explorer makes an image with its settings.
The first row of the image
